⚠️ Dependency awareness (important)

Cart depends on:

Redis
Catalogue

👉 Kubernetes won’t guarantee they’re ready

What happens:
cart starts → redis not ready → initial failures

👉 Your probes will handle this — good design 👍
-----------
⚠️ Missing Redis port (depends on app)

You only passed:

REDIS_HOST: "redis"

👉 Some apps need:

REDIS_PORT: "6379"
-------------
kubectl get pods -n roboshop
